One minute drive to I-95, Route 29, Route 100, the B/W Parkway. A few miles to BWI, Ft. Meade, Arundel Mills and Columbia Town Center. We invite you to schedule your personal tour of your new home today.

Description: Welcome to home sweet home, surrounded by a beautiful, park-like landscape. Very spacious 1, 2, and 3 bedroom floor plans in unique styles with unsurpassed customer service. Conveniently located on Route 1, minutes from I-95, Fort Meade, NSA, Baltimore-Washington Parkway and the Intercounty Connector (ICC) providing easy access to the Capital Beltway, downtown Washington D.C. and downtown Baltimore. Come relax at Country Meadows and enjoy a long list of amenities including our fully equipped fitness center, sauna, sparkling swimming pools, 2 playground areas, tennis court and car wash area. The other ABC’s...Affordable, Beautiful, Comfortable, Convenient, Customer Servicing, you've made an excellent choice!

Description: Enclave at Emerson offers its residents all of the comforts of home without having to own. Enjoy prime Howard County location with top-notch schools and an abundance of parks, trails and recreational areas. Rent one of our beautiful apartments or spacious townhomes and let us take care of the rest. Our emergency maintenance team is here to help at all hours of the day, and our clubhouse and amenity spaces are here for your enjoyment. Join us for resident events to mingle with neighbors or just enjoy a stroll around the community with your family. Enjoy all of the advantages of being a homeowner, plus more, when you call Enclave at Emerson home.

Description: Located in the center of Maryland and the Nation’s Capital, Ashbury Courts brings convenience and luxury to North Laurel, Maryland in Howard County. Located right on Route 1, Ashbury Courts Apartments, a pet friendly community, offers incredibly convenient access for commuters to greater DC and Baltimore with the best value of any apartment building in the area. We are close to Fort Meade, I-95 and the Beltway. Fitness Room, Media Room and Billiards Room with NO AMENITY FEES. All kitchens have granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and wood floors. If you are looking for the best deal in the area, look no further. We have the nicest living space for the most reasonable prices. Ashbury Courts offers Condo living at affordable apartment pricing.Six Reasons Why You Should Choose Us: 1.	Health Club-style Fitness Center 2.	Granite & Stainless Steel in Kitchens 3.	Outdoor seating and BBQ Areas 4.	Full-sized Washers & Dryers 5.	Controlled Access Entry 6.	First Floor Retail

Description:
(970) 331-4037 - 3BR/2BA UPDATED END OF THE ROW TOWNHOUSE IN LAUREL - Beautiful Three Bedroom, Two Bathroom Updated End of Row Townhouse in Laurel features a first floor with gorgeous laminate hardwood flooring throughout a spacious living room, separate dining room. There is a full bath with walk in shower and a fully equipped kitchen with pantry closet, and updated appliances including dishwasher and updated cabinets. The second floor has new carpeting throughout three spacious bedrooms and a full hall bath. Below is a fully finished basement club room with separate laundry/storage area with washer/dryer included. Outside has a spacious patio for entertaining. Tenants have access to a neighborhood rec center that requires membership!
Pets Considered on a case by case basis with additional Security Deposit!

Beautiful 3 Bedroom Town home offering convenience, comfort & charm! This home has 3 full bathrooms and is located in the Howard County Wydemere Community of Laurel, Maryland. Upper level Master bedroom w/ Walk in closet and full bathroom. Enjoy the conveniences of Howard County schools, Hospitals and colleges. Community recreation areas that include: parks and playgrounds. Easy access to Interstate 95, Main Street MARC Train station, restaurants, libraries; close to Ft. Meade and the new Laurel Town Center. Available for rent NOW so do not wait! Schedule your tour today!

First, let's look at its size: huge end unit with 4 large bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bathrooms. Over 3200 square feet!

Large bedrooms (each fits a full size bed!) Two car garage. 
With so many great features, this townhouse will go very quickly. Don't miss this opportunity. Schedule a showing today!
NOTE: Two year lease preferred!
